{"tid":913993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國公民遇害,侵侵應否派兵剷平North Sentinel Island?","createTime":"2018-11-24T00:47:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-24T02:37:43.000Z","uid":163207,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f5320c21e463b62e80ac608f27188a31837c6ae2","tid":913993,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T00:47:51.000Z","msg":"教化啲無知民族,為世界文明出一分力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"859f302e506a17e3213bb4c29b97d8190aea3113","tid":913993,"uid":163207,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T00:50:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181122/1312289.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20181122%2F1312289.htm&d=oPV7m1N%2BLefFuRADm1MhdGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=74ecbb15\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181122/1312289.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n桑提內爾人對外界抱持強烈敵意，動輒用弓箭或石塊攻擊來往飛機和船隻，使外人難以靠近。安達曼警察局長帕達（Dependra Pathak）表示，目前還沒有辦法收回周約翰的遺體，但強調警方已經聯絡人類學家和熟悉當地部落的專家共同制定計畫，會想辦法將周約翰的遺體帶回。當地警方已經依謀殺罪立案調查，並逮捕7名涉案人士。警方沒有公布涉案人士姓名，但透露7人全都是漁民。<br />\n<br />\n捉唔到啲生蕃搵漁民祭旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53fa5d31ad8a034736588e95f731a22de76a3995","tid":913993,"uid":49215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T00:53:19.000Z","msg":"整個飛彈過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0dd1cb3fdc7b3335e185cb686bc503be423a0ae","tid":913993,"uid":64060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T01:14:30.000Z","msg":"支那一樣，衰過生蕃"},{"pid":"f0408a8350d3cfbfa61c045c4fe0d0f7ff76925f","tid":913993,"uid":163207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f0dd1cb3fdc7b3335e185cb686bc503be423a0ae","tid":913993,"uid":64060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T01:14:30.000Z","msg":"支那一樣，衰過生蕃"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T02:31:12.000Z","msg":"好好多,八國聯軍一打到即刻夾道歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8bb6dc75bcc1d02ecf3751da534c36f34068e6a","tid":913993,"uid":163207,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f0408a8350d3cfbfa61c045c4fe0d0f7ff76925f","tid":913993,"uid":163207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f0dd1cb3fdc7b3335e185cb686bc503be423a0ae","tid":913993,"uid":64060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T01:14:30.000Z","msg":"支那一樣，衰過生蕃"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T02:31:12.000Z","msg":"好好多,八國聯軍一打到即刻夾道歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T02:33:50.000Z","msg":"八國聯軍中德俄兩軍被普遍認為在鎮壓義和團暴亂中最為野蠻兇悍，而且軍紀較差，而美日軍隊被認為「嚴守紀律，不擾居民」。當時北京滿大街都是居民自製的太陽旗及「Belong Japan（日本所有）的標語」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc227a17c2ed79d95a59261a10ddbd87ecb63bfc","tid":913993,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T02:37:43.000Z","msg":"中國人是最愛國的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n聯軍占領津京後，當地排洋、仇洋的風氣大變，街頭一改人人包紅布、穿紅衣義和團打扮，天津百姓家門首皆插白旗，行人亦各持白旗，上寫「某某國戶人」，或「某某國順民、良民」。北京商鋪爭先貼出保護單，各國占管區居民，紛紛向洋兵送萬民傘，時人記載：「昔則挾刃尋仇、滅此朝食，今乃忝顏娟敵，載道口碑，京師及各省都會，其翻譯通事之人，聲價驟增，勢力極盛，於是都中之人，咸歆而慕之，昔之想望科舉者，今皆改而從事於此途。」"}]}